Package: tidydrc
Type: Package
Title: Tidy modelling of dose-response relationships with the drc package
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Angel Angelov
Maintainer: Angel Angelov <aangeloo@gmail.com>
Description: Tidy wrapper for the drc package.
